snippet.description:
Swastima Khadka & Samragyee RL Shah | It's My Show With Oshin Sitaula | 22 June  2024

Kantipur TV HD को कार्यक्रम It's My Show With Oshin Sitaula मा यो साता  Swastima Khadka & Samragyee RL Shah र ओशिन सिटौलाको साथमा !

About It's My Show :

The legacy of It's My Show with Oshin Sitaula accompanied by a live band where she invites celebrated people on the sets and gets the house on fire with her wit and charm has finally come back with a brand new season,

It's My Show with Oshin Sitaulais a new hit Nepali television talk show. In this program, Oshin interviews various guests from various fraternity by inviting them to the program's set. Like every TV programs hosted by Oshin Sitaula, It's My Show has been superhit Nepali show from it's first episode and liked by Nepalese and Non-Nepalese throughout the world. It is the first program in Kantipur TV since it has gone HD. This episode of It's My Show withOshin Sitaula was broadcasted on Kantipur TV HD at 9:00pm on 22 June  2024.

It's My Show with Oshin Sitaulais a new hit Nepali television talk show. In this program, Oshin interviews various guests from various fraternity by inviting them to the program's set. Like every TV programs hosted by Oshin Sitaula, It's My Show has been superhit Nepali show from it's first episode and liked by Nepalese and Non-Nepalese throughout the world. It is the first program in Kantipur TV since it has gone HD. This episode of It's My Show withOshin Sitaula was broadcasted on Kantipur TV HD at 9:00pm on 22 June  2024.

snippet.description:
Bamboo stores water in its hollow segments for survival. From my observations, you can find this water in young stalks, particularly those near water sources or after prolonged heavy rains. The water undergoes natural filtration through the plant's roots and tissues, giving it a slightly sweet taste and making it drinkable. The young bamboo tissue is quite easy to pierce with a knife. Simply make one or two holes (at the top and bottom) to enjoy the refreshing bamboo water!

snippet.description:
And so, I became yours, before I was even myself. The melody wrote the words, the words sang the melody, as if everything was to always return to find me as yours. As time refused to change directions, space bent itself to place me in front of you so I could fall in love the way love was meant to be fallen into.

In one way or the other, in some time or another, as I have found myself in front of you, I shall always find myself as yours.

For Maya, always.
